01:38.681 --> 01:40.183
<i>But at some point...</i>

01:42.185 --> 01:43.520
<i>you kind of have to wonder...</i>

01:43.520 --> 01:46.397
No! No!

01:46.397 --> 01:47.398
No!

01:49.442 --> 01:51.194
<i>...was the treasure an escape?</i>

01:57.283 --> 01:58.493
<i>Or was it a trap?</i>

