<i>♪ Require from us a song ♪</i>

03:14.277 --> 03:18.323
<i>♪ How can we sing King Alpha's song ♪</i>

03:18.323 --> 03:22.285
<i>♪ In a strange land? ♪</i>

03:22.285 --> 03:23.786
