03:23.786 --> 03:25.622
Rescue?

03:25.622 --> 03:27.207
From what? From...

03:28.374 --> 03:29.334
from paradise?

03:29.918 --> 03:31.544
I'm not going back.

03:32.128 --> 03:33.004
Ever.

03:33.922 --> 03:36.716
