05:12.186 --> 05:13.354
-  You ready?
-  Yeah.

05:13.354 --> 05:15.106
All right. Today's the day.

05:15.106 --> 05:18.401
All right, remember, watch your shadow.
They see that, they're gone.

05:18.401 --> 05:20.320
