- Right there!

06:18.252 --> 06:19.629
Eleven o'clock.

06:19.629 --> 06:21.130
Just under the horizon.

06:23.383 --> 06:25.134
I think it's
just the whitecaps on the reef.

06:25.134 --> 06:27.220
You don't know that.
It's right there. I see it.

06:27.220 --> 06:29.389
- Sarah, Sarah, hey, hey.
- What if it's...

06:29.389 --> 06:31.599
No, it's... it's... it's not your dad.

06:31.599 --> 06:33.226
It's not your brother. Okay?

06:34.185 --> 06:35.186
I promise.

06:35.686 --> 06:37.397
No, I'm sure.

06:38.356 --> 06:39.357
