12:37.631 --> 12:38.716
Come on.

12:43.512 --> 12:44.680
-  Whoo!
-  Hey!

12:45.848 --> 12:47.516
-  We did it!
-  Oh man.

12:48.017 --> 12:49.393
-  Hello, hello.
- Hey there.

12:49.393 --> 12:51.896
